column4: Excited for our (@MiRoCampbell & @brauerlab1) new paper in @NatureHumBehav about the effects of exposing people to their peers’ pro-diversity attitudes on inclusion and the achievement gap. https://t.co/Wqabit1VXv via @uwmadison
Thanks @BoazHameiri and @JinXunGoh. It's taken years to get it done, but totally worth it! Such is the reality of science in the field!
